a national historic site. * {{ill|Kitsunezuka Kofun (Nichinan)|ja|狐塚古墳 (日南市)}} ({{ill|Nichinan|ja|日南市}}, {{ill|Miyazaki Prefecture|ja|宮崎県}}).
