aft}}, {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県|12=draft}}) - Part of the {{ill|Sone Archaeological Site Cluster|ja|曽根遺跡群|1=Sone Sites|12=draft}}; a national historic site. * {{ill|Nakabaru Kitsunezuka Kofun|ja|中原狐塚古墳|12=draft}} ({{ill|Kurume|ja|久留米市|12=draft}}, Fukuoka) - An ornamental kofun within the {{ill|Tanushimaru Kofun Cluster|ja|田主丸古墳群|12=draft}}; a national historic site. * {{ill|Kitsunezuka Kofun (Nichinan)|ja|狐塚古墳 (日南市)|12=draft}} ({{ill|Nichinan|ja|日南市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Miyazaki Prefecture|ja|宮崎県|12=draft}}).
